{
  "stem": "7238.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it was soon over.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Quietly, we had to form-- those who were on the side for work had to go on a five ahead-- five-deep line, walking.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "This was a terrible march.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We didn't know where we were going, why we were going, and what will be the end of it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But we walked through the Jewish quarter in such an eerie silence there-- a place where little children played, where it's always very noisy-- no one.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We walked for a long, long time, not saying a word, until we came to a big factory.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "This was the place where they sorted us out-- men separate, women on the other side.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We were assigned to a big hall in a factory, sitting on a cold floor, waiting for what's going to be the next.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They didn't give us food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They didn't talk to us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We didn't talk either.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And then a new march-- the march to the small ghetto, to the real ghetto.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I have to mention that on our way through the streets, the Poles were lined up on both side, clapping hands and jumping for joy they are getting rid of the Jews.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Those were our neighbors.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We arrived at the ghetto, and were assigned places where we will live.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We came into a small, little house with two rooms only.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Once, this was the poorest neighborhood where Jews lived.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Once there lived a tailor, and he probably raised family and was happy.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But we walked into an empty place-- 10 people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And we were so exhausted, so tired.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Everybody looked for a place to sit down.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Some three smart girls found a bed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They were fortunate.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I found a table where the tailor cut his material, and put my tired body down there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we waited.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
